quran[16{c,v,t}:
15,16,"yeh hamari car farmai hai ke aasman mein hum ne bohat se mazboot qilay banaye, unn ko dekhnay walon ke liye muzayyan kya"
15,17,aur har shetan mardood se un ko mehfooz kar diya
15,18,"koi shetan un mein raah nahi pa sakta, ila yeh ke kuch sun gun le le aur jab woh sun gun lainay ki koshish karta hai to aik shola roshan uss ka peecha karta hai"
15,19,"hum ne zameen ko phelaya, uss mein pahar jamaye, is mein har noo ki nabataat theek theek napi tali miqdaar ke sath ugai"
15,20,"aur is mein maeeshat ke asbaab faraham kiye, tumahray liye bhi aur unn bohat si makhloqaat ke liye bhi jin ke Razaq tum nahi ho"
15,21,"koi cheez aisi nahi jis ke khazanay hamaray paas nah hon, aur jis cheez ko bhi hum nazil karte hain aik muqarrar miqdaar mein nazil karte hain"
15,22,"baar aawar hawaon ko hum hi bhaijtay hain, phir aasman se pani barastee hain, aur uss pani se tumhe sairaab karte hain iss doulat ke khazana daar tum nahi ho"
15,23,"zindagi aur mout hum dete hain, aur hum hi sab ke waris honay walay hain"
15,24,"pehlay jo log tum mein se ho guzray hain unn ko bhi hum ne dekh rakha hai, aur baad ke anay walay bhi hamari nigah mein hain"
15,25,"yaqeenan tumhara rab un sab ko akhatta kere ga, woh hakeem bhi hai aur Aleem bhi"
15,26,hum ne ensaan ko stri hui matti ke sokhey gaaray se banaya
15,27,aur uss se pehlay junoo ko hum aag ki lapat se peda kar chuke thay
15,28,"phir yaad karo uss mauqa ko jab tumahray rab ne firshton se kaha ke"" mein sari hui matti ke sokhey gaaray se aik bashar peda kar raha hon"
15,29,"jab mein ussay poora bana chukun aur is mein apni rooh se kuch phoonk dun to tum sab is ke agay sjday mein gir jana """
15,30,chunancha tamam firshton ne sajda kya
15,31,siwaye iblees ke ke uss ne sajda karne walon ka sath dainay se inkaar kar diya
